verse.lines:
Waiting on the Lord,
  for the promise given;
Waiting on the Lord
  to send from heaven;
Waiting on the Lord,
  by our faith receiving;
Waiting in the upper room.

Waiting on the Lord,
 giving all to Jesus;
Waiting on the Lord,
  till from sin He frees us;
Waiting on the Lord
 for the heav'nly breezes;
Waiting in the upper room.

Waiting on the Lord,
  longing to mount higher;
Waiting on the Lord,
  having great desire;
Waiting on the Lord
  for the heav'nly fire;
Waiting in the upper room.
